H0.text: Which river enters the sea at Whitby in Yorkshire. Tees

H3.text: Which river enters the sea at Whitby in Yorkshire. Esk

A4.text: Whitby is situated on the east coast of Yorkshire facing the North Sea in a deep valley at the mouth of the River Esk.
